  <brief_title>Lifestyle Intervention for Prevention of Gastric Neoplasm</brief_title>
  <official_title>Positive Lifestyle Interventions for the Prevention of Gastric Pre-cancer and Cancer Occurrences in Patients With Chronic Atrophy Gastritis and Reccurence of Gastric Cancer After Edoscopic Resection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
