  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether positive life style interventions (such as
      diet modification and smoking cessation) are effective in the prevention of gastric
      pre-cancer and cancer occurrences and reccurence of gastric cancer after edoscopica
      resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
