  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of chronic atrophy gastritis proved by gastroscopy biopsy pathology or early
             gastric cancer patients who have recieved endoscopic resection

          -  have one or several bad lifestyle habits such as eating too much salt, eating too few
             fruits, smoking, drinking wine, and lack of sleep.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients who refuse to change lifestyle according to the trial plan
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
